收标准\n    36\t\n    37\t> 以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/match
ing.feature`。\n    38\t\n    39\t```gherkin\n    40\tFeature: Card Recommendati
ons\n    41\t  Scenario: User sees recommendation cards\n    42\t    Given the u
