nts.length - 1].updated_at.toISOString()\n    : null;\n```\n`userParticipants` a
re ordered by `updated_at DESC`. The last one is the oldest. The cursor is the o
ldest updated_at. Then next query uses `updated_at < :cursor`. This correctly ge
ts older conversations. This is correct.\n\nLet me check more files.',
